     <div type="to_the_reader">
   <pb facs="4"/>
   <head>To the Christian Reader, health in the Lord.</head>
   <lg>
      <l>Reade to gaine thereby.</l>
      <l>Iudge indifferently.</l>
      <l>Repent vnfeignedly.</l>
      <l>Receiue instruction willingly.</l>
      <l>Meditate thereon zealously.</l>
      <l>Lest you enter into temptation carelesly.</l>
   </lg>
   <closer>Vale in Christo.
<signed>Iohn Andrewes.</signed>
   </closer>
